    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The mechanism for running the WebSocket Protocol over a single stream of an HTTP/2 connection is equally applicable to HTTP/3, but the HTTP-version-specific details need to be specified.  This document describes how the mechanism is adapted for HTTP/3.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
